General.Name: Story-I Limited
General.Description: Story-I Limited, through its subsidiary, PT Inetindo Infocom, operates as a reseller and retailer of Apple and IT lifestyle products and services. It also offers service and maintenance for Apple devices. The company operates through 25 stores in 10 cities of Indonesia under the Story-I branded stores. Story-I Limited was incorporated in 2013 and is headquartered in West Leederville, Australia.
